ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCarcross/Tagish First Nation Self-Government Agreement, the Champagne and Aishihik First Nations Self-Government Agreement and the Kluane First Nation Self-Government Agreement
PrecisOrder consenting to the amendment of Self-Government Agreements by the Carcross/Tagish First Nation, the Champagne and Aishihik First Nations, and the Kluane First Nation in order to enable the First Nations to register parcels of Settlement Land in the Yukon Land Titles system.
